<div class="card card--informative m-b-md">
	<h3 class="h4">Claim the OLEV Grant</h3>
	<p>Do you want to reduce the cost of your chargepoint by Â£500, by claiming the OLEV Grant?</p>
	<div class="radios-wrap">
		<div class="radio-wrap radio-wrap--inline">
			<input data-radio-open-panel="olevPanel" type="radio" name="olevDiscount" id="yesOlevDiscount" value="yesOlevDiscount"/>
			<label for="yesOlevDiscount" class="radio">Yes</label>
		</div>
		<div class="radio-wrap radio-wrap--inline">
			<input data-radio-close-panel="olevPanel" type="radio" name="olevDiscount" id="noOlevDiscount" value="noOlevDiscount" checked="checked"/>
			<label for="noOlevDiscount" class="radio">No</label>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div id="olevPanel" data-js-module="toggleAccordionPanel" class="accordion-panel accordion-panel--md">
		<hr class="m-t-lg m-b-lg">
		<p class="p-b-lg bold">You need to qualify for all of the below criteria in order to be eligible for the OLEV grant. Please check all the boxes that apply to you.</p>
		<div class="field-row">
			<div class="checkboxes-wrap">
				<div class="checkbox-wrap">
					<input type="checkbox" name="ownVehicle" id="ownVehicle">
					<label for="ownVehicle">I ordered, own or lease an electric vehicle</label>
				</div>
				<div class="checkbox-wrap">
					<input type="checkbox" name="orderedAfter" id="orderedAfter">
					<label for="orderedAfter">
						My Vehicle was purchased after the 1st of April 2015
						<br>
						<span class="font-style-small">(If the vehicle is a company car, a letter from the company is required as evidence)</span>
					</label>
				</div>
				<div class="checkbox-wrap">
					<input type="checkbox" name="offStreetParking" id="offStreetParking">
					<label for="offStreetParking">I have private, off-street parking at my domestic property</label>
				</div>
				<div class="checkbox-wrap">
					<input type="checkbox" name="rightOfWayCable" id="rightOfWayCable">
					<label for="rightOfWayCable">The cable, when run from the chargepoint to the car, will not cross a public right of way</label>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="buttons-container">
			<button class="button">Claim OLEV grant</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>